article_title: More than 43,000 killed in Gaza since 7 October 2023 - Hamas-run health ministry.
sentence: At  least  43,061  people  have  been  killed  in  the  Gaza  Strip  since  7  October  2023,  the  Hamas-run  ministry  of  health  in  the  territory  says  in  its  latest  estimate.
